    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ was completed but does not compensate for model form and validation relevance gaps. The overall credibility package is assessed as insufficient for regulatory submission supporting a Class III VAD hemolysis claim at MRL 5. Package accepted into the evidence repository for documentation purposes pending remediation.",
